Street Tempura specialise in build your own noodle or rice box, itâs pretty straightforward and thereâs an ample amount of choices to select from! We got the stir fried noodles with tempura chicken and egg fried rice with tempura chicken and sweet & sour sauce. This was hands down the most delicious tempura we have tasted, perfectly cooked on the inside with the crispiest batter! Everything was of high quality, made freshly and also had that Indo-Chinese taste to it! We preferred the noodles to the rice as they tasted much better with the tempura in our opinion. 

Ordered the wasabi chips as well, as they were something we had never tried! Definitely go for it if you want some extra spice on your chips! 

Lastly, the dessert we got from here is certainly a game changer! Tempura fried ice cream ð¤¤ Itâs so good, you just have to try it! We went for the rocky road topping with nutella sauce. 

We strongly recommend that you order Street Tempura for your next takeaway!
